 nature; because of approaching the right goal, they soon become free from all material lust. In the \u003cem\u003eŚrīmad-Bhāgavatam\u003c/em\u003e it is recommended that whether one is a pure devotee and is free from all material desires, or is full of material desires, or desires liberation from material contamination, he should in all cases surrender to Vāsudeva and worship Him. As stated in the \u003ca href=\\\"/en/library/sb/2/3/10/\\\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eBhāgavatam\u003c/em\u003e (2.3.10)\u003c/a\u003e:\"},{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"verse_text\",\"id\":2264,\"bb\":2007,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/7/20/b2007/\",\"body_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eakāmaḥ sarva-kāmo vā\u003cbr /\u003emokṣa-kāma udāra-dhīḥ\u003cbr /\u003etīvreṇa bhakti-yogena\u003cbr /\u003eyajeta puruṣaṁ param\u003c/em\u003e\"},{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"paragraph\",\"id\":2265,\"bb\":2008,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/7/20/b2008/\",\"body_value\":\"$42\"}]}],\"short_title\":\"Bg. 7.20\",\"medium_title\":\"Bhagavad-gītā As It Is 7.20\"},{\"id\":2266,\"meta\":{\"type\":\"books.Verse\",\"slug\":\"21\",\"show_in_menus\":false,\"seo_title\":\"\",\"search_description\":\"\",\"first_published_at\":null,\"alias_of\":null,\"locale\":\"en\"},\"title\":\"TEXT 21\",\"advanced_view_url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/7/advanced-view/#bb2009\",\"language_menu\":[{\"display_name\":\"አማርኛ (Ethiopian)\",\"language_code\":\"am\",\"enabled\":false,\"url_path\":\"/am/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Български (Bulgarian)\",\"language_code\":\"bg\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/bg/library/bg/7/21/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Čeština (Czech)\",\"language_code\":\"cs\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/cs/library/bg/7/21/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Dansk (Danish)\",\"language_code\":\"da\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/da/library/bg/7/21/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Deutsch (German)\",\"language_code\":\"de\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/de/library/bg/7/21/\"},{\"display_name\":\"English\",\"language_code\":\"en\",